videos.description: Devon Hall drives to the rim and throws up a wild shot to get the and-1 basket.
videos.headline: Virginia's Hall makes a tough layup

videos.description: Devon Hall sizes up his man then drives to his left and finishes with his right hand through contact for the basket.
videos.headline: Virginia's Hall gets another and-1

videos.description: Nigel Johnson attempts a floater but Sagaba Konate grabs the shot out of the air.
videos.headline: WVU's Konate gets a monster block

videos.description: Kyle Guy on two straight possessions hits a three from the wing and the corner to give Virginia the lead.
videos.headline: Virginia's Guy drills back-to-back 3s
